"Upgrade “%@”’s home storage?" = "Upgrade “%@”’s home storage?";
"This workspace's home folder currently lives in a macOS folder shared into the VM. Bromure can move it onto a private ext4 disk image instead.\n\nWhy: suspended workspaces resume without confused tools (files keep their identity across suspend/resume), git repositories in the home are no longer exposed to shared-folder corruption, and the image automatically shrinks on your Mac as files are deleted inside the VM.\n\nThe move happens once, during the next boot — a large home can take a few minutes, with progress shown on the boot screen. Your current home folder is kept on the Mac as a backup." = "This workspace's home folder currently lives in a macOS folder shared into the VM. Bromure can move it onto a private ext4 disk image instead.\n\nWhy: suspended workspaces resume without confused tools (files keep their identity across suspend/resume), git repositories in the home are no longer exposed to shared-folder corruption, and the image automatically shrinks on your Mac as files are deleted inside the VM.\n\nThe move happens once, during the next boot — a large home can take a few minutes, with progress shown on the boot screen. Your current home folder is kept on the Mac as a backup.";
